HandyJORM.model

Class ModelAttributesCollection

  • java.lang.Object
    • HandyJORM.model.ModelAttributesCollection
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<ModelAttribute>

    public class ModelAttributesCollection
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<ModelAttribute>
    Created by DeiGray on 09/05/2017. Collection of attribute in a model. This collection represent in a group each model-attributes, and store information's about modelAttribute coategorie (primary key, foreign key, etc. Each model get one MAC to store informations about its own attributes. Implements Iterable, so you can foreach the into the class.
